{"route":{"route":"/posts/7d547224/","outputPath":"posts/7d547224/index.html","kind":"post","title":"gpg使用","language":"zh-Hans","params":{"abbrlink":"7d547224"}},"description":"生成一个密钥 之后会选择加密方式, 有效期, 用户名及邮箱, 密码, 按自己需求填就行了. 创建一个子密钥 导出密钥 导出子密钥 导出吊销证书 删除密钥 导入子密钥 查看密钥 加密文件 解密 GPG 加密解密简明教程 GPG 的正确使用姿势","post":{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/gpg使用.md","route":"/posts/7d547224/","abbrlink":"7d547224","title":"gpg使用","date":"2020-10-02 14:00:01","updated":"2020-10-02 14:00:01","tags":["Linux","Encrypt"],"categories":["Linux"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"","moreAnchor":"more","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"<p>生成一个密钥</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">gpg</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> --full-gen-key</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>之后会选择加密方式, 有效期, 用户名及邮箱, 密码, 按自己需求填就行了.</p>\n<p>创建一个子密钥</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">gpg</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> --edit-key</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\"> [key </span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">hash]</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">gpg</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">> </span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">addkey</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#6A737D\">#只有与前面是相同的, 按需求选择.</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">gpg</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">> </span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">save</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#6A737D\"># 保存</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>导出密钥</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">gpg</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> -o</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> /path/gpg_key</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> --export-secret-keys</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\"> [key </span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">hash]</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>导出子密钥</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">gpg</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> -o</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> /path/gpg_key.sub</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> --export-secret-subkeys</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\"> [key </span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">hash]</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>导出吊销证书</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">gpg</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> --generate-revocation</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\"> [key </span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">hash]</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#6A737D\"># 输出是文本内容, 复制保存下来就行了</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><span id=\"more\" class=\"post-more-anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><br>\n删除密钥</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">gpg</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> --delete-secret-keys</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\"> [key </span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">hash]</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">gpg</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> --delete-keys</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\"> [key </span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">hash]</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>导入子密钥</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">gpg</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> --import</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> /path/gpg_key.sub</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>查看密钥</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">gpg</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> -k</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">gpg</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> -K</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>加密文件</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">gpg</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> -r</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\"> [user </span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">name]</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> -o</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\"> [output </span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">file]</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> -e</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\"> [filename]</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>解密</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">gpg</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> -o</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\"> [output </span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">file]</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> -d</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\"> [filename] </span><span style=\"color:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#6A737D\"># 输出到文件</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">gpg</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> -d</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\"> [filename] </span><span style=\"color:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#6A737D\"># 直接输出到终端</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<hr>\n<p><a href=\"https://gist.github.com/jhjguxin/6037564\">GPG 加密解密简明教程</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mogeko.me/2019/068/\">GPG 的正确使用姿势</a></p>\n","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"7d547224","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false}}